description: The Northwest Florida Daily News Varsity app is a must-have mobile app for sports fans living, working and enjoying all the Emerald Coast has to offer. Get real time high school sports news and alerts, and stay connected wherever you go with Northwest Florida Daily News Varsity apps.  Access local sports news and stories around the clock from our trusted writers, plus, photos, videos, news alerts and much more. Simple design helps you find your sports information quickly and easily. Stay updated in the world of varsity sports no matter where you are or what you are doing.  Customize your sports news and favorites with “My Sports.” Share sports information through E-Mail, Facebook and Twitter. If you like our Varsity Apps spread the word to friends on Facebook and Twitter.
